#As a user I would like to see a list of bookmarks displayed
#As a user I would like to be able to add new bookmarks
#As a user I would like to be able to delete bookmarks
#As a user I would like to be able to comment on bookmarks
#As a user I would like to be able to tag bookmarks into categories
#As a user I would like to be able to be able filter through the list of bookmarks by category
#As a user I should only be able to see and manage my bookmark contribution


#Domain Model
  #Nouns: User, list, bookmarks and category
  #Verbs: See, add, delete, comment, tag, filter and manage
